<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>لَطَارَتْ وَلَوْ أَنِّي دُعِيْتُ لِقَرْبَةِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>لَكُنْتُ كَذِي رِجْلَيْنِ رِجلٌ صحيحةٌ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>ورِجلٌ رَمَى فِيْهَا الزَّمَانُ فَشَلَّتِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَقَائِلَةٍ لِمَا رَأَتْ مَا أَصَابَنِي<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَمَا أنَا فِيْهِ مِن لَهِيبٍ وَزَفْرَتِي<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>رُوَيْدَك لا تَقْنُطْ وَإِنْ كَثُرَ الخَطََا<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَلا تَيْأسَنْ مِن نَيْلِ رَوْحٍ وَرَحْمَةِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>مَعَ العُسْرِ يُسْرٌ وَالتَّصَبُّرُ نُصْرَةٌ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَلا فَرَجٌ إِلا بِشِدَّةِ أَزْمَةِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c1">"وَكَمْ عَامِلِ أَعْمَالَ أَهْلَ جَهَنَّمٍ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>فَلَمَّا دَعَى المَوْلى أُعِيْدَ لِجَنَّةِ"<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c1">"فَقُلْتُ لَهَا جُوزِيتِ خَيْرًا على الذي<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>مَنَحْتِ مِنَ البُشْرَى وَحُسْنِ النَّصِيحَةِ"<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c1">"فَهَلْ مِنْ سَبِيلِ لِلْنَجَاةِ مِنَ الرَّدَى<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَمَا حِيْلَتِي في أنْ تُفَرَّجَ كُرْبَتِي"<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c1">"فَقَالَتْ فَطِبْ نَفْسًا وَقُمْ مُتَوَجِّهًا<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>لِربَّكَ تَسْلَمْ مِنْ بَوَارٍ وَخَيْبَةِ"<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c1">"فَكَمْ آيِسٌ مِنْ رَحْمَةِ اللهِ فالتْجَا<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>إليه فَحُطَّتْ عَنْهُ كُلُّ خَطِيئَةِ"<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>"فَدَيْتُكَ فَأقْصِدْهُ بِذُلٍّ فَإِنَّهُ ...<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>